      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to list this absolute beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it feels like it just left the dealership! It\u2019s been garage-kept and pampered since day one, so you\u2019re getting a ride that\u2019s virtually spotless and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019ve been looking for a car that\u2019s been treated with nothing but love and care, you\u2019ve found it. Drop me a message\u2014I'd love to see this go to a great home!",
      "price": 46800.0,
